title: NewCast - November 2021
description:
" برترین های نوامبر "

سلام من مختار رزمجو هستم

 عنوان : November 2021

 مود : شاد / عاشقانه / کریسمسی

 ژانر: پاپ / راک / الکترونیک و ...

http://hamibash.com/playlistpodcast

02-Jasmine Thompson, Calum Scott - love is just a word

03-Aaron Lewis - Pull Me Under

04-Sia - Sing for My Life

06-Alan Walker, Winona Oak - World We Used To Know

07-Cat Power - Pa Pa Power

08-chloe moriondo feat. Thomas Headon, Alfie Templeman - Dizzy 

09-Oliver Tree feat. Ty Dolla $ign - Life Goes On (feat. Ty Dolla $ign) Remix

10-Cole Swindell, Lainey Wilson - Never Say Never

11-Seeb, Nina Nesbitt - Sweet Dreams & Dynamite

12-Cheat Codes, Lee Brice, Lindsay Ell - How Do You Love 

13-Alan Walker, Benjamin Ingrosso - Man On The Moon

14-Post Malone, The Weeknd - One Right Now

15-Masked Wolf, Bebe Rexha - It’s You, Not Me

19-Dynoro - Swimming In Your Eyes
